Introducing Tensor:
Google intelligence on a chip.
Utilising Google's expertise in AI and ML, we created a brand new technology platform to deliver a more helpful, intelligent and personalised Pixel than ever before. Find out how Tensor's data-centre-calibre ML, image processor, security and contextual awareness help anticipate, recognise and respond to your individual needs.
Google-powered machine learning

Using Google's cutting-edge ML models, Tensor was designed with Google Research to unlock advanced photography, security and speech capabilities that weren't possible before – like instantly transcribing and accurately translating any video that you watch.3


Using Google's most advanced deep learning neural network algorithms, Tensor puts state-of-the-art speech recognition and language translation in your pocket. Designed to handle the intensive computing needs of bigger and better models right from your Pixel, translation quality is improved by 18% on average to help you better understand and communicate in languages other than your own.7 And because these algorithms run on-device rather than through a network and server, they work fast – no Internet connection required.4

Custom image signal processor

The new Pixel camera system taps into Tensor's powerful processing, custom ISP and advanced machine learning to apply the next era of Pixel's camera magic to your photos and videos.


We built Google's Live HDR+ tone-mapping technology, low-light video and custom auto-focus engine directly into Tensor's ISP so that you can capture the moment just as you experienced it – in clear, vivid detail.


Tensor also helps make signature Pixel features like Night Sight, Live HDR+ and video stabilisation even better – and brings them to the most popular social apps for the very first time.

Context hub

With Tensor's specialised always-on computing hub, your Pixel is more personal and intuitive than ever before. The context hub was designed to provide contextualised help and process low power tasks with incredible efficiency for great battery life.


Tensor helps Pixel surface the content you need, when you need it – all while remaining secure and private. Simply glance at Pixel's always-on display to find out when you need to leave for your next appointment, or see what song is playing with Now Playing song detection – now up to three times faster.

Secure to the core

Tensor provides a new layer of Google-designed hardware security with its custom, isolated security core subsystem. The security core works with the next-gen Titan M2™ co-processor to make Pixel even more resilient to attacks.6


With the most layers of hardware security in any phone,9 Tensor enables Pixel to protect your personal and sensitive information through end-to-end vertical integration.
